               <p>A Second Count, for that the said 
               <persName id="t17840114-53-person560">
                  Thomas
                   Eaton
               <interp inst="t17840114-53-person560" type="surname" value="Eaton"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840114-53-person560" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840114-53-person560" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , on the said 6th of November, was possessed of, and entitled unto certain shares, to wit 750 l. and that he the said 
               <persName id="t17840114-53-person561">
                  John
                   Ash
               <interp inst="t17840114-53-person561" type="surname" value="Ash"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840114-53-person561" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840114-53-person561" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , afterwards, falsely, deceitfully, and feloniously, did personate the said 
