            , on the said 4th of November, was<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178401140068"></xptr> possessed as foresaid, and the said John Ash well knowing the premises, afterwards, to wit, on the same day the same place, did personate the said 
               <persName id="t17840114-53-person567">
                  Thomas
                   Eaton
               <interp inst="t17840114-53-person567" type="surname" value="Eaton"></interp>
